games.comment: Arian Foster actually led the team in rushes (13 for 34 yards), but most of that came in the 4.h quarter.    The Seahawks never really had a chance.
Arian Foster sustaining a hamstring injury. Foster managed just 9 yards on 3 attempts. I hope you didn't draft Foster, as he was an obvious candidate to get hurt, thanks to his horrific diet.
